HEADWORD: Pollicate
<hw>Pol"li*cate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>pollex</ets>, <ets>pollicis</ets>, a thumb.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Having a curved projection or spine on the inner
